(135, '_transient_dash_c05853b002c443ec8e57ff884f56cdde', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://es.wordpress.org/2017/05/22/noticias-y-eventos-wordpress-para-la-semana-21-17/''>Noticias y eventos de la semana</a> <span class="rss-date">22 Mayo, 2017</span><div class="rssSummary">¬°Buenos d√≠as a todos! Os dejamos algunas noticias y el listado de las Meetups para esta semana. Meetups 24/05 ‚Äì Barcelona¬†‚Äì Hardening WordPress like a Hacker con Chema Alonso 25/05 ‚Äì Barcelona ‚Äì¬†WPML support desk representative Yvette Oliveau, will give presentation 25/05 ‚Äì Tarragaona ‚Äì¬†Diferencias entre WordPress.COM y WordPress.ORG 25/05 ‚Äì M√°laga ‚Äì¬†Comercio electr√≥nico en [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://ma.tt/2017/05/boarding-wrong-flight/''>Matt: Boarding Wrong Flight</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://ma.tt/2017/05/ibm-goes-non-remote/''>Matt: IBM Goes Non-Remote</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://poststatus.com/wordpress-higher-education-rachel-cherry-draft-podcast/''>Post Status: WordPress in higher education, with Rachel Cherry ‚Äî Draft Podcast</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class="dashboard-news-plugin"><span>Plugin popular:</span> Limit Login Attempts&nbsp;<a href="plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=limit-login-attempts&amp;_wpnonce=f7572fcdcd&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800" class="thickbox open-plugin-details-modal" aria-label="Instalar Limit Login Attempts">(Instalar)</a></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
